info.description: Welcome in Neji! =================== > **Note:** > - We can not give assurance about security due to their policies. > - This is package mainly used to upload your fiel into online world. > - This will help you to send the your file in directory into online world. > - This package uses the some extra site in order to cloud store. ## Version ```python import neji print(neji.Neji_version()) # output: Hydrogen-0.0.0.1 ``` ## Usage ```python import neji print(neji.Neji_upload(r"C:\...\Pictures\trial\black1 - Copy (5).png")) # output: https://file.io/CfJlLI ``` ## Contributing Pull requests, we are welcome.
